  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b93\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three arrested with swords near Vavunia Omanti fuel station",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police said three people were arrested with swords near the Vavunia Omanti petrol station.",
        "People have been waiting in long queues on the road for days to get fuel at the Omani filling station.",
        "In this case, the group of youths united and formed a new line, and today when fuel was distributed at the filling station, they were involved in a fight saying that they should supply fuel to their line.",
        "However, the police reached the spot and brought the situation under control, arrested three people involved in the incident and recovered the swords and guns hidden in the car."
      ],
